{"tid":2039240,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS! OnePlus 8 Pro黑科技 濾鏡具有透視能力","createTime":"2020-05-28T02:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T07:37:55.000Z","uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53c6161e590c7441632f8f579fea2f4a1ed4790b","tid":2039240,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TuFiM35.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTuFiM35.gif&h=e0022932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/0ebcl5vgmsy41.jpg?width=640&amp;crop=smart&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=56b91230a1e8e203cb5ca1a8ad99997fc1339592\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2F0ebcl5vgmsy41.jpg%3Fwidth%3D640%26crop%3Dsmart%26auto%3Dwebp%26s%3D56b91230a1e8e203cb5ca1a8ad99997fc1339592&h=72240f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.androidinfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/OnePlus-8-Pro-Camera-Color-filter-see-through-Platsic-Remote.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidinfotech.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FOnePlus-8-Pro-Camera-Color-filter-see-through-Platsic-Remote.jpg&h=960b1503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2020/05/19/200519-40450-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2020%2F05%2F19%2F200519-40450-2.jpg&h=016117f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cOsylGr2_h4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FcOsylGr2_h4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=e17f96ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb7214a249f2527eea4f268887f3e412616d3bb","tid":2039240,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"old"},{"pid":"d82f69a58cbe5fdc0c07f23803ea16910526ba5f","tid":2039240,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"前陣子 YouTuber Unbox Therapy 在測試 OnePlus 8 Pro 的內建相機，使用「秋意」濾鏡時，發現這款濾鏡針對某些材質會拍出「透視」的效果，也因此引起使用者疑慮，表示這樣的拍攝效果可能會造成隱私的問題，對此 OnePlus 官方也發表了回應。<br />\n<br />\n從 Unbox Therapy 的測試影片中可以看到，當把物品放在黑色衣服底下拍攝時，套用「秋意」濾鏡就可以隱約看到衣服下的物品，關於這個濾鏡有「透視」的效果，OnePlus 表示當初在開發 OnePlus 8 Pro 的濾光鏡頭時，希望可以針對紅外線感光，搭配「秋意」濾鏡，讓使用者可以拍出特殊的紅外線照片。<br />\n<br />\n但後來許多用戶發現這款濾鏡可以透視一些塑膠、衣物材質，如果穿了某些可透視材質的衣物，使用這款鏡頭就會被拍出衣物底下的身體，因此產生了一些隱私上的爭議，對此 OnePlus 除了表示歉意之外，也會透過手機軟體更新的方式取消這款濾鏡，但由於仍有許多用戶很喜歡這個濾鏡呈現的效果，所以會持續改善，消除大家的疑慮之後再重新提供，不知道大家對這款濾鏡有什麼想法呢？Hanne 覺得看起來很酷，但如果真的被一些人拿去做不當的使用就違背 OnePlus 一開始的本意了，不過還是很期待這款濾鏡改善之後可以重新上架啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://agirls.aotter.net/post/57386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aotter.net%2Fpost%2F57386&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=87269cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://agirls.aotter.net/post/57386</a>"},{"pid":"0bd11a61574396772b3383a3bf11318b6e8edb03","tid":2039240,"uid":226655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"勁閪咩<br />\n佢粒cam只係冇裝紅外filter乍<br />\n係算被動式紅外sensor<br />\n<br />\n你求其攞部機，插鳩咗個infrared filter咪得lor<br />\n<br />\niPhone個faceid可以主動釋放紅外光添<br />\n但系統層面唔俾你睇咋嘛"},{"pid":"1264b194a456756052415c800681dd6441d17656","tid":2039240,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bd11a61574396772b3383a3bf11318b6e8edb03","tid":2039240,"uid":226655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"勁閪咩<br />\n佢粒cam只係冇裝紅外filter乍<br />\n係算被動式紅外sensor<br />\n<br />\n你求其攞部機，插鳩咗個infrared filter咪得lor<br />\n<br />\niPhone個faceid可以主動釋放紅外光添<br />\n但系統層面唔俾你睇咋嘛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\